Welcome to the Amazing Tattoo Ideas free Gallery

 Hi I'm Ady a Huge tattoo lover, and with my partner in crime Lucy (see above) we bring you a cool place to view different types of tattoos from around the world, and hopefully you will get some inspiration for your next piece of INK

 We have spent a lot of time going over your feedback and comments and applied many of the features that you have requested. We hope you like the NEW gallery layout, better image quality and less force closing issues. (fingers crossed)

So as a little appreciation for Lucy's hard work and late nights working on the app all we ask is you rate the app with a nice comment.

This way we can keep the app FREE for all the fans. All 950,000+ of you, and growing..WOW

Anyway what is NEW!

 Gallery layout is new, better quality images, You can save All photos to Sd Card and Gallery Folder. You can share or show off the tattoos on your facebook page. Send them to friends by email, MMS etc..

 If you have feedback please email us via the feedback button, please do not leave a bad rating/comment, otherwise we cannot fix the problem

If you're a hardcore tattoo lover, then why not try our premium Tattoo Magazine app with regular updated articles, HD galleries, Videos and Much More.. all about INK and Tattoo Culture

 Anyway enough of us.

P.S Remember please leave a good rating/comment. You Guys Rock!

Lucy and Ady XX
